# Review Checklist

## Architecture

- [ ] Controller hanya parse input dan call service
- [ ] Service berisi business logic
- [ ] Repository hanya query DB, soft delete
- [ ] Error handling centralized, format RFC 7807
- [ ] AppError digunakan (dari `src/lib/errors.ts`)

## Code Quality

- [ ] Tidak ada `any` type
- [ ] All function memiliki return type
- [ ] Input validation dengan Zod

## Security

- [ ] Ownership check ada di service layer
- [ ] Parameterized query digunakan
- [ ] Sensitive data tidak di-log
- [ ] Password hash tidak pernah di-return

## Testing

- [ ] Service layer punya unit test
- [ ] Happy path coverage
- [ ] Error case coverage

